DescShort: Melee, Moderate DMG (Smash), Foe -Res (All), -Dmg, Combo Builder
DescLong: You deftly strike your foe in a very vulnerable location. Rib Cracker deals Moderate Damage but reduces your foe's Damage and Resistance moderately for a short time. Rib Cracker is a Combo Builder and adds 1 Combo Level. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Fast.
